# Project Structure Guide

This project is for the **Dota 2 Meta Hero Grid Updater**, a Windows desktop app to automate updating Dota 2 hero grids.

## Key Documents
- [PRD.md](mdc:memory-bank/PRD.md): Product requirements, user stories, and feature list.
- [implementation-plan.md](mdc:memory-bank/implementation-plan.md): Step-by-step implementation plan for the app.
