- [architecture.md](mdc:memory-bank/architecture.md): (Currently empty) Intended for high-level architecture notes.
- [progress.md](mdc:memory-bank/progress.md): (Currently empty) Intended for tracking project progress.

## Main Features (see [PRD.md](mdc:memory-bank/PRD.md) and [implementation-plan.md](mdc:memory-bank/implementation-plan.md))
- UI for selecting hero grid type and updating config
- Automatic SteamID detection and config path management
- Backup and replace of hero grid config
- Windows Task Scheduler integration for weekly updates
- Error handling, notifications, and logging

All source code and UI implementation details are to be added in the main project directory (not present yet). See the above documents for guidance on structure and features.
